reviewText: GREAT OLD-SCHOOL WRESTLING GUEST WHO THE PROMOTE WHAT? YOU MUST BUY THIS DVD, YOU WOULD BELIEVE THE STARS! IF THERE IS ANY DVD WRESTLING YOUR GOING TO BUY IS IT!!
Great seeing matches I've never seen esp the weird cage match. Video and sound quality not that great at times though.
Great classic wrestling and great promos too
Lots of good matches. Not the same old ones,that are normally on 80's dvds. Worth watching,best i have in this series.
Awesome get DVD for true wrestling fans very rare.getting to see flair and brody not on the  . Mainland.thank you highspot

I did not know that any footage of Polynesian Championship Wrestling ever existed. I was happy to find this and hoping to see a lot more. Packed with tons of top names due to Hawaii being between Japan and the west coast. Great DVD a must see for any wrestling buffs.
